      <h2>Message from the owner</h2>
<p><strong> Progressive Microtechnology, Inc.</strong> (PMI)  has been serving the needs of the barcode industry since 1984 as a software developer and a dealer of barcode equipment and supplies. We have also been providing law enforcement with the easiest to use, most flexible evidence management system for the past 16 years. We are a Veteran-owned small business and <a href="http://nefla.bbb.org/codbrep.html?wlcl=y&amp;id=154154755&amp;cons=y">a member of the Better Business Bureau</a>. PMI carries a full range of barcode products from all the major manufacturers. We are dedicated to serving you professionally with our whatever-it-takes attitude, while providing terrific savings on barcode scanners, label printers, barcode readers, software, portable data collectors, barcode labels, ribbons and other related products. Thank you for visiting our site!</p>
      <p>Best Regards,</p>
